A group representing the league attended the trial of Nicholas Ninow in the Pretoria High court in the capital Pretoria. Ninow admitted to raping a seven year old girl twice in a toilet cubicle in a Dros restaurant in Silverton in Pretoria. 

The recent rape and murder of University of Cape Town film and media student, Uyinene Mrwetyana, is also  one of the brutal attacks on women that have put issues of gender-based-violence in the spotlight. . The League's Nosipo Tlhobeku-Makeke ... --SABC--